<item>
            <title>[SOLR-346] need to improve snapinstaller to ignore non-snapshots in data directory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-346</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mail-archive.com/solr-user@lucene.apache.org/msg05734.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.mail-archive.com/solr-user@lucene.apache.org/msg05734.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; latest snapshot /opt/solr/data/temp-snapshot.20070816120113 already&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; installed&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A directory in the Solr data directory is causing snapinstaller to fail.  Snapinstaller should be improved to ignore any much non-snapshot as possible.  It can use a regular expression to look for snapshot.dddddddddddddd where d is a digit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
